OL,5, A man seriously hurt in the Manchester 
OL,6, Arena bombing said he is staying "true 
OL,7, to his promise" to take the paramedic  
OL,8, who saved his life to watch Manchester 
OL,9, United in an FA Cup final.             
OL,11,FMartin Hibbert from Chorley, Lancashire
OL,12,Fmade the promise to paramedic Paul     
OL,13,FHarvey after the pair became friends.  
OL,15,FMr Hibbert said he "would definitely   
OL,16,Fnot be here today" without the         
OL,17,Ftreatment he received from Mr Harvey.  
OL,19,F"Paul made decisions that night which  
OL,20,Fultimately saved my life," he said.    
